{"id": 59498, "date": "2025-08-27T04:00:35", "date_gmt": "2025-08-27T11:00:35", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59498"}, "modified": "2026-05-14T13:28:23", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-14T20:28:23", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-august-27-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/27/kingdom-of-days-august-27-2/", "title": {"rendered": "August 27"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1970:\u00a0</strong>Steel Mill rehearses in Wanamassa, New Jersey for their upcoming appearance in Nashville.</p>\n<p><strong>1979:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and his studio team work on the mix for &#8220;Ramrod&#8221; at the Power Station in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their fifth show of a six-night stand at the Los Angeles Memorial Sports Arena.</p>\n<div id=\"v-OUrIQLcR-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/OUrIQLcR?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"54171\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/simi_valley_star_1981_08_30_4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Simi_Valley_Star_1981_08_30_4-scaled.jpg?fit=1699%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1699,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Simi_Valley_Star_1981_08_30_4\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Simi_Valley_Star_1981_08_30_4-scaled.jpg?fit=680%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-54171\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Simi_Valley_Star_1981_08_30_4.jpg?w=758&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3969\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-0827/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1981-0827.gif?fit=189%2C250&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"189,250\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-0827\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1981-0827.gif?fit=189%2C250&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3969 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1981-0827.gif?resize=189%2C250&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"189\" height=\"250\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the band play their second of two Born in the U.S.A. shows at CNE Stadium in Toronto.</p>\n<div id=\"v-LRMoo2CB-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/LRMoo2CB?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1987:</strong> Bruce joins Cats on a Smooth Surface at their gig at Tradewinds in Sea Bright, playing &#8220;Light of Day&#8221; and a selection of covers including &#8220;Proud Mary,&#8221; &#8220;Fortunate Son,&#8221; &#8220;If You Need Me,&#8221; &#8220;Around and Around,&#8221; and &#8220;Lucille.&#8221;</p>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the reunited E Street Band wrap their five-night stand at Boston&#8217;s Fleet Center, tour debuting &#8220;Raise Your Hand&#8221; in the encores with Peter Wolf.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8D06CtXE5y4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28962\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1999-08-27a-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1999-08-27a.png?fit=333%2C1755&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"333,1755\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1999-08-27a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1999-08-27a.png?fit=194%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28962 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1999-08-27a.png?resize=333%2C1755&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"333\" height=\"1755\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1999-08-27a.png?w=333&amp;ssl=1 333w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1999-08-27a.png?resize=57%2C300&amp;ssl=1 57w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 333px) 100vw, 333px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20693\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1999-08-27b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1999-08-27b.png?fit=1657%2C694&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1657,694\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1999-08-27b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1999-08-27b.png?fit=758%2C318&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20693 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1999-08-27b.png?resize=758%2C317&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"317\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1999-08-27b.png?w=1657&amp;ssl=1 1657w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1999-08-27b.png?resize=300%2C126&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1999-08-27b.png?resize=1024%2C429&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1999-08-27b.png?resize=768%2C322&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1999-08-27b.png?resize=1536%2C643&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band wrap their west coast Rising Tour swing with a show at San Jose&#8217;s Compaq Center.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/z33OKND7IA8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20695\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2002-08-27/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-27.png?fit=1283%2C1806&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1283,1806\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2002-08-27\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-27.png?fit=727%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20695 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-27.png?resize=758%2C1067&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-27.png?w=1283&amp;ssl=1 1283w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-27.png?resize=213%2C300&amp;ssl=1 213w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-27.png?resize=727%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 727w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-27.png?resize=768%2C1081&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2002-08-27.png?resize=1091%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1091w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2021:\u00a0</strong>Bruce calls into\u00a0<em>The Wild and the Innocent</em> on E Street Radio to mark the show&#8217;s tenth anniversary, broadcast live from Asbury Park.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/aQfLYn64y40?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>That evening,\u00a0<em>Springsteen on Broadway</em> continues its limited return engagement at the St. James Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Bruce and the E Street Band wrap up their Boston Reunion stand with the long-awaited return of encore favorite, &#8220;Raise Your Hand.&#8221; More highlights inside.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 12358, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false}, "categories": [2], "tags": [147, 558, 25, 424, 640, 489, 200, 367, 376, 128, 625, 28, 1000], "class_list": ["post-59498", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-kingdom-of-days", "tag-born-in-the-usa", "tag-born-in-the-usa-tour", "tag-boston", "tag-canada", "tag-cats-on-a-smooth-surface", "tag-los-angeles", "tag-peter-wolf", "tag-reunion-tour", "tag-rising-tour", "tag-river-tour", "tag-san-jose", "tag-toronto", "tag-waitin-on-a-sunny-day"], "aioseo_notices": [], "jetpack_publicize_connections": [], "jetpack_featured_media_url": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/19990827_front.jpg?